 other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/18249/', '', 'Glipizide, Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Tolazamide, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Tolbutamide, Miglitol, More', 'Ethotoin, Brivaracetam, Methsuximide, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Eslicarbazepine, Phensuximide, Ganaxolone, Methylphenobarbital, More', 1767369485);
